like when shared and lets you force Facebook to re-scrape the page.",[17,45,46],{},"What about LINE? In the early days, no — you had to throw the link into LINE just to see what it'd look like.",[17,48,49],{},"The real issue — when you need to update a link's preview, you'll find LINE keeps serving the old preview no matter how many times you re-share:",[17,51,52],{},[38,53],{"alt":54,"src":55},"Stale preview","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-04%2013.02.42.png",[17,57,58],{},"Eventually LINE refreshes on its own — but for a marketing team, those 30 minutes are gold.",[17,60,61],{},"The fix is LINE's \"Page Poker\" tool.",[17,63,64,65],{},"Link: ",[28,66,67],{"href":67,"rel":68},"http:\u002F\u002Fpoker.line.naver.jp\u002F",[32],[12,70,72],{"id":71},"line-page-poker","LINE Page Poker",[17,74,75,76,80],{},"Usage is dead simple — open the ",[28,77,79],{"href":67,"rel":78},[32],"Page Poker"," link. The UI is minimal:",[17,82,83],{},[38,84],{"alt":79,"src":85},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-04%2013.05.36.png",[17,87,88,89,93],{},"Paste your URL, pick the locale and region, and check ",[90,91,92],"strong",{},"Clear Cache",":",[17,95,96],{},[38,97],{"alt":92,"src":98},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-04%2013.07.04.png",[17,100,101],{},"Hit submit. Now share the link to LINE again and you'll see the updated preview:",[17,103,104],{},[38,105],{"alt":106,"src":107},"Fresh preview","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-04%2013.07.58.png",[17,109,110,113],{},[28,111,79],{"href":67,"rel":112},[32]," also previews how your link will render — same idea as Facebook's debugger:",[17,115,116],{},[38,117],{"alt":118,"src":119},"LINE preview","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-04%2013.08.59.png",[17,121,122],{},[38,123],{"alt":124,"src":125},"Facebook preview","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-04%2013.09.13.png",[17,127,128,129,132],{},"PS: For Facebook cache busting, use the ",[28,130,33],{"href":30,"rel":131},[32]," and click \"Scrape Again\":",[17,134,135],{},[38,136],{"alt":137,"src":138},"Facebook scrape again","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-03-04%2013.11.17.png",{"title":140,"searchDepth":141,"depth":141,"links":142},"",2,[143,144,145],{"id":14,"depth":141,"text":15},{"id":22,"depth":141,"text":23},{"id":71,"depth":141,"text":72},"Misc","2022-03-04 12:54:09","LINE is everywhere as a sharing channel, but once a link's been shared, LINE caches the preview aggressively — and there's no obvious way to bust the cache. Until you discover Page Poker. This post covers LINE's official Page Poker tool for clearing link preview cache, plus Facebook's Sharing Debugger as the equivalent for Facebook.","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002Fclear-line-link-preview-cache-with-page-poker","1",{"title":6,"description":148},false,"en\u002FMisc\u002Fclear-line-link-preview-cache-with-page-poker",[159,160,161,162],"meta","LINE","Cache","Facebook",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F03\u002F04\u002Fclear-line-link-preview-cache-with-page-poker\u002F","zZh3styoxtraoZUfMRMXE47hniDlUshlAlNhpAAkchU",{"newer":167,"older":171},{"url":168,"title":169,"date":170},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F03\u002F05\u002Fmango-frontend-18-mongoose-static-methods\u002F","Mongoose Static Methods: They Look Like Instance Methods, But They're Not","2022-03-05 20:46:18",{"url":172,"title":173,"date":174},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F03\u002F03\u002Fmango-frontend-17-mongoose-instance-methods\u002F","Mongoose Instance Methods: Add Your Own Methods to a Document","2022-03-03 08:43:27",[176,181,186],{